            <title>[LU-6184] Interop 2.6.0&lt;-&gt;2.7 sanity test_102q: flistxattr size: No such file or directory</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6184</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/c4795558-a7bd-11e4-bc9c-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/c4795558-a7bd-11e4-bc9c-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_102q failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;orphan_linkea_check
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;client:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 102q: flistxattr should not return trusted.link EAs for orphans == 05:09:53 (1422450593)
flistxattr size: No such file or directory
 sanity test_102q: @@@@@@ FAIL: orphan_linkea_check 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_102q was added from &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/12884/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/12884/&lt;/a&gt;   should do version check,   do does test_102r&lt;/p&gt;</description>
